00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,100
Kir?

244
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:28,299
Tn. Domon?

245
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:30,799
Sudah waktunya kita melakukan wawancaranya.

246
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:33,100
Ya, kurasa begitu.

247
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:42,499
Permisi.

248
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:44,499
Bisakah kau mundur sedikit?

249
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:46,700
Kami ingin merekam wawancaranya.

250
00:12:21,300 --> 00:12:22,500
Penyiram air?

251
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,600
Hujan?

252
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:51,100
Hei, ayolah. Yang benar saja.

253
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,500
Sungguh?

254
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:58,699
Ayo, dan duduklah.

255
00:12:58,700 --> 00:12:59,800
Cepat!

256
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:03,000
Terima kasih.

257
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:13,199
DJ memakai payung biru tua.

258
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,399
Bisakah aku menembaknya?

259
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,699
Tunggu.

260
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:19,199
Menembak dia melalui payung akan mengurangi akurasi.

261
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,399
Tapi sungguh aneh.

262
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,500
Tidak hujan di sisi sini.

263
